pix (2.4.2) tricia; urgency=medium

  [ Michael Webster ]
  * print settings: Fix inch-to-metric conversion
  * print settings: Remove 'pixel' option in units selector. It is confusing because it's treated *exactly* the same as millimeters, and doesn't make much sense as a physical unit of measure even if it was properly calculated.
  * print settings: Keep images centered until explicitly moved off center (or Custom is explicitly selected).  It makes no sense to have the center combobox revert to Custom when adjusting the image size.

